THE GAME
--------

  'MiniKonnex' is a Workbench game where you have to connect all
tiles of the game board, by rotating links around the tiles so
they connect with the links of neighbouring tiles.

  The general principle of this game is the same as that of
'Konnex', another of my Workbench games. However, for
'MiniKonnex', the entire game board is shown in the game window...

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-3 game board sizes to play with: 5 by 5 tiles, 7 by 7 tiles and
 9 by 9 tiles size.

-A game you can play while waiting for other tasks to complete...
 or just for fun!

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50 kilobytes, so
 it takes little time to download ...although, you can play
 another of my Workbench games while downloading this game ;)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

